ial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/TCHM/111%2c%e4%b8%8a%e8%a8%b4%2c574%2c20220621%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"TCHM,111,上訴,574,20220621,1","JYEAR":"111","JCASE":"上訴","JNO":"574","JDATE":"20220621","JTITLE":"毒品危害防制條例"}